sequenceDiagram
    participant T as timerfd
    participant M as pmu_monitor
    participant P as pmu_counters
    participant L as lbr ring buffer
    participant O as CSV output
    participant Y as Python feature pipeline

    T->>M: tick every interval_ms
    M->>M: poll() wakeup and compute elapsed_ms
    M->>P: pmu_read()
    P-->>M: delta counters + multiplex scaling
    M->>L: lbr_drain()
    L-->>M: sample_count / avg_span
    M->>M: output_compute_lbr()
    M->>O: output_csv_row()
    O-->>M: append one CSV row
    M->>Y: later load CSV rows
    Y->>Y: drop inst=0 rows
    Y->>Y: convert 5 counters to MPKI
    Y->>Y: read lbr_log1p_span
    Y->>Y: pad/truncate and apply Z-score
    Y-->>M: tensors X_v1 / X_v2 / Y
